<title type="html"><![CDATA[The Ruling on Oral Sex]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=1157&amp;p=1223#p1223"><![CDATA[
<strong><span style="font-size: 200%; line-height: normal">The Ruling on Oral Sex</span></strong><br /><em>Shaikh Ahmad an-Najmi and Shaikh al-Albani</em><br /><br /><strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Question:</span></strong> What is the Ruling on Oral Sex?<br /><br /><strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Answer:</span></strong> “As for a woman sucking the private part of a man, then this is haram not allowed. This is because a man will ejaculate and when he ejaculates prostatic fluid will be emitted and it is impure by consensus. So if it enters her mouth then her stomach, then sometimes it can lead to sickness. <strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Shaikh Bin Baz passed the verdict that it is haram and I heard him verbally</span></strong>”<br /><br /><em>[Asilah Dhil-Qarnayn al-Andunisi pg. 3]</em><br /><br /><strong><span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: normal">Translator’s Note:</span></strong><br /><br />Shaikh al-Albani rahimahullah said in regards to oral sex:<br /><br /><strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Questioner:</span></strong> “In regards to kissing the private part of the woman?<br /><br /><strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Shaikh:</span></strong> Kissing?<br /><br /><strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Questioner:</span></strong> Yes<br /><br /><strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Shaikh:</span></strong> This is the action of dogs”.<br /><br /><em>[Silsilatul-Huda wal-Noor no. 174]</em><br /><br />Translated by<br /><br />Faisal Ibn Abdul Qaadir Ibn Hassan<br />Abu Sulaymaan<br /><br />Source: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://darussaafi.wordpress.com/2015/08/01/the-ruling-on-oral-sex-shaikh-ahmad-an-najmi-and-shaikh-al-albani/">https://darussaafi.wordpress.com/2015/0 ... al-albani/</a><!-- m --><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=56">Shehzad Sattar</a> — Sat Feb 25, 2017 5:32 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
